  OpenShift Container Platform Cluster Limits

    Limit Type                          3.9 Limit
    ---------------------------------------------
    Number of nodes                     2K
    Number of pods                      120K
    Number of pods per node             250
    Number of pods per core             10 is the default value. The maximum supported value is the number of pods per node.
    Number of namespaces                10K
    Number of pods per namespace        15K
    Number of services                  10K
    Number of back-ends per service     5K
    Number of deployments per namespace 20K


